@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Academics";
}

<div class="container bg-light p-4 rounded mt-4">
    <div class="jumbotron text-center bg-primary text-white p-5 rounded">
        <h1 class="display-4">Academic Programs</h1>
        <p class="lead">Discover our diverse range of academic programs designed to inspire and educate.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row my-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/images/primary_education.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" alt="Primary Education">
            <h2>Primary Education</h2>
            <p>
                Our primary education program focuses on building a strong foundation in core subjects such as Mathematics, Science, and Languages. We aim to foster a love for learning through engaging and interactive teaching methods.
            </p>
            <p>
                Students participate in hands-on activities, group projects, and educational games that make learning fun and meaningful. Our dedicated teachers ensure that each child receives personalized attention to support their individual growth.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/images/secondary_education.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" alt="Secondary Education">
            <h2>Secondary Education</h2>
            <p>
                The secondary education program prepares students for higher education and future careers. We offer a comprehensive curriculum that includes a variety of subjects, extracurricular activities, and career guidance.
            </p>
            <p>
                Students have the opportunity to explore their interests and develop skills in areas such as technology, arts, and sports. Our career counseling sessions help students make informed decisions about their future educational and career paths.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="row my-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/images/higher_secondary_education.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" alt="Higher Secondary Education">
            <h2>Higher Secondary Education</h2>
            <p>
                Our higher secondary program offers specialized streams in Science, Commerce, and Humanities. Students receive in-depth knowledge and skills in their chosen fields, preparing them for university and professional life.
            </p>
            <p>
                We provide state-of-the-art laboratories, libraries, and resources to support advanced learning. Students engage in research projects, internships, and seminars to gain practical experience and insights into their chosen careers.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/images/extracurricular_activities.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" alt="Extracurricular Activities">
            <h2>Extracurricular Activities</h2>
            <p>
                We believe in the holistic development of students. Our school offers a range of extracurricular activities, including sports, arts, music, and drama, to help students discover and nurture their talents and interests.
            </p>
            <p>
                Participation in extracurricular activities promotes teamwork, leadership, and creativity. Students can join various clubs and teams, participate in competitions, and showcase their talents in school events and performances.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="row my-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/images/special_education.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" alt="Special Education">
            <h2>Special Education</h2>
            <p>
                We are committed to providing inclusive education for all students. Our special education program supports students with learning disabilities and other special needs, ensuring they receive the necessary resources and guidance to succeed.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our team of special educators, counselors, and therapists work closely with students to create personalized learning plans. We provide a supportive and nurturing environment where every student can thrive and reach their full potential.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/images/adult_education.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" alt="Adult Education">
            <h2>Adult Education</h2>
            <p>
                Our adult education program offers courses for lifelong learners. Whether you are looking to acquire new skills, pursue a hobby, or continue your education, we have a variety of courses designed to meet your needs.
            </p>
            <p>
                Courses are available in subjects such as computer literacy, language learning, and vocational training. Our flexible schedules and experienced instructors make it easy for adults to balance learning with their other responsibilities.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
